caption.p: Effect of intraperitoneal injection of Ruta graveolens L. extract and rutin on serum malondialdehyde level; RG30, RG100 and RG300: groups treated with 30, 100 and 300 mg/kg of R. graveolens extract; ###significant difference between control group and other groups ( p < 0.001), *significant difference between rutin group and extract ( p < 0.05).
